title: Vortex Juice Bar and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mostly vegetarian and vegan food except for fish: rice bowls, wraps, quesadilla, chili, soup and salad, kids' menu. Offers rice milk, soy milk, and oat milk option. Extensive fresh raw juices selection. Small place with several tables inside.
